MD5 HASHTRAY — is a simple, lightweight utility that lives in your system tray and provides instant MD5 hash calculations for any file. This minimalistic tool integrates seamlessly with Windows Explorer, allowing you to right-click any file and instantly generate its MD5 checksum. Perfect for developers, security professionals, and anyone who needs to verify file integrity quickly without opening complex applications.

