    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    MD5 HashTray is a compact utility that runs silently in your Windows system tray, consuming minimal system resources. It integrates directly with Windows Explorer's context menu, adding a "Calculate MD5" option when you right-click any file. When selected, it quickly reads the file, computes its MD5 hash using optimized algorithms, and displays the result in a small popup window with one-click copy functionality. The program supports files of any size and handles large files efficiently without memory issues .
    
