    🔹 HASH CALCULATION

    🔐 SUPPORTED ALGORITHMS
    • MD5: Standard 128-bit hash
    • SHA-1: 160-bit secure hash
    • SHA-256: 256-bit secure hash (optional)
    • SHA-512: 512-bit secure hash (optional)
    • CRC32: Quick checksum verification
    
    🔹 EXPLORER INTEGRATION

